<div class="subtitle">Welcome to BOM experiments</div>

<p>
  Here you will find all kinds of experiments with public data from the Australian Bureau of Meteorology.
  The objective of this project is to provide a useful presentation of weather information (such as temperature) combined with local and context specific data (such as local temperature sensors).
</p>
